    ---help---
    IDH_HTML_TCPIP_HTTP_NO_AUTH_WITHOUT_SSL
    ---endhelp---

config TCPIP_HTTP_MAX_DATA_LEN
    int "Max Data Length (bytes) for Reading Cookie and GET/POST Arguments"
